---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="ja">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main class="pt-0">
			<section class="hero-section">
				<div class="glow"></div>
				<div class="laser-beam" style="--rotation: 0deg;"></div>
				<div class="laser-beam" style="--rotation: 45deg;"></div>
				<div class="laser-beam" style="--rotation: -45deg;"></div>
				<div class="laser-beam" style="--rotation: 90deg;"></div>
				<div class="laser-beam" style="--rotation: -90deg;"></div>
				<div class="laser-beam" style="--rotation: 135deg;"></div>
				<div class="laser-beam" style="--rotation: -135deg;"></div>
				<div class="laser-beam" style="--rotation: 180deg;"></div>
				<h1 class="hero-title">Vision</h1>
				<p class="hero-subtitle">
					地上から宇宙まで、エネルギーが途切れない世界をつくる。<br>
					― 月面探査にも届く光無線給電インフラを実現する ―
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="section">
				<h2 class="section-title">Mission</h2>
				<div class="content-box max-w-5xl mx-auto bg-transparent shadow-none">
					<p class="text-xl text-center">レーザー無線給電でエネルギーの束縛を解き、人類の進歩を加速する。</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="section">
				<h2 class="section-title">Value</h2>
				<div class="content-box max-w-5xl mx-auto bg-transparent shadow-none">
					<p class="text-xl text-center">
						"Battery & Cable-Free" を安全・精密に。<br>
						私たちは〈安全性 / 革新 / 共創 / 持続可能性〉を軸に、レーザー技術で社会インフラをアップデートします。
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="section">
				<h2 class="section-title">事業内容</h2>
				<div class="content-box max-w-5xl mx-auto bg-transparent shadow-none">
					<p class="text-lg text-center">
						レーザー光を用いた光無線給電システムの研究開発・製造・販売・リース・保守を主軸に、AI画像処理による高精度レーザー追尾ソフトウェア、ドローン搭載用受電モジュール、エネルギーマネジメント回路の設計受託、さらに宇宙探査向け電力インフラの実証までを一気通貫で手掛けます。
					</p>
					<p class="text-lg mt-4 text-center">
						技術コンサルティングやデータ標準化支援を含むSaaS / サブスクリプション型サービスにより、閉鎖空間点検から月面ミッションまで ― エネルギーの新しい流れをデザインします。
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	:root {
		--primary-color: #00b4d8;
		--secondary-color: #ff6b35;
		--text-color: #2b2d42;
		--background-start: #e0f7fa;
		--background-end: #fff3e0;
	}

	body {
		margin: 0;
		padding: 0;
		font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--background-start), var(--background-end));
		color: var(--text-color);
		min-height: 100vh;
		overflow-x: hidden;
	}

	main {
		margin: 0;
		padding: 0;
		width: 100%;
		overflow-x: hidden;
	}

	.hero-section {
		padding: 0;
		text-align: center;
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
		height: 100vh;
		width: 100%;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		justify-content: center;
		align-items: center;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.hero-title {
		font-size: 6rem;
		font-weight: 900;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 180, 216, 0.3);
		transform-style: preserve-3d;
		perspective: 1000px;
		animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
		position: relative;
		z-index: 2;
	}

	.hero-title::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: -20px;
		left: -20px;
		right: -20px;
		bottom: -20px;
		background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));
		opacity: 0.1;
		filter: blur(20px);
		z-index: -1;
		animation: pulse 4s ease-in-out infinite;
	}

	.hero-subtitle {
		font-size: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		width:100vw;
		max-width: 1000px;
		z-index: 2;
	}

	.section {
		padding: 4rem 2rem;
		max-width: 100%;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.section:first-of-type {
		margin-top: 4rem;
	}

	.section-title {
		font-size: 3rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		margin: 0 auto;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		position: relative;
		display: block;
		text-align: center;
		background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
	}

	.section-title::after {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		bottom: -10px;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translateX(-50%);
		width: 100px;
		height: 4px;
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));
		border-radius: 2px;
	}

	.content-box {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
		padding: 3rem;
		border-radius: 20px;
		box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.content-box.bg-transparent {
		background: transparent;
		box-shadow: none;
		backdrop-filter: none;
	}

	.content-box.bg-transparent::before {
		display: none;
	}

	.glow {
		position: absolute;
		width: 300px;
		height: 300px;
		background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--primary-color) 0%, transparent 70%);
		opacity: 0.3;
		filter: blur(30px);
		animation: glow 8s ease-in-out infinite;
	}

	.laser-beam {
		position: absolute;
		width: 100%;
		height: 2px;
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(0, 180, 216, 0.3), transparent);
		opacity: 0;
		filter: blur(1px);
		animation: laser 8s ease-in-out infinite;
		transform-origin: center;
		z-index: 1;
	}

	.laser-beam:nth-child(2) {
		animation-delay: 1.2s;
	}

	.laser-beam:nth-child(3) {
		animation-delay: 2.4s;
	}

	.laser-beam:nth-child(4) {
		animation-delay: 3.6s;
	}

	.laser-beam:nth-child(5) {
		animation-delay: 4.8s;
	}

	.laser-beam:nth-child(6) {
		animation-delay: 6s;
	}

	.laser-beam:nth-child(7) {
		animation-delay: 7.2s;
	}

	.laser-beam:nth-child(8) {
		animation-delay: 8.4s;
	}

	.laser-beam:nth-child(9) {
		animation-delay: 9.6s;
	}

	@keyframes float {
		0%, 100% {
			transform: translateY(0) rotateX(0);
		}
		50% {
			transform: translateY(-20px) rotateX(5deg);
		}
	}

	@keyframes glow {
		0%, 100% {
			transform: translate(0, 0);
		}
		50% {
			transform: translate(100px, 100px);
		}
	}

	@keyframes pulse {
		0%, 100% {
			opacity: 0.1;
			transform: scale(1);
		}
		50% {
			opacity: 0.2;
			transform: scale(1.1);
		}
	}

	@keyframes laser {
		0%, 100% {
			opacity: 0;
			transform: scale(0) rotate(var(--rotation));
		}
		15% {
			opacity: 0.6;
			transform: scale(1) rotate(var(--rotation));
		}
		35% {
			opacity: 0.6;
			transform: scale(1) rotate(var(--rotation));
		}
		50% {
			opacity: 0;
			transform: scale(1) rotate(var(--rotation));
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.hero-title {
			font-size: 3rem;
		}
		.hero-subtitle {
			font-size: 1.4rem;
		}
		.section {
			padding: 4rem 1rem;
		}
		.section-title {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}
		.content-box {
			padding: 2rem;
		}
	}
</style>
